                  <handDesc>
                     
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Fine, regular.</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red (vivid vermilion).</seg>
                        Scribe: Za-Walda Māryām. Za-Walda
                        Māryām is mentioned as the scribe in the supplication formula on <locus target="#65vc">65vc</locus>, 110rc, 141vc, 171ra, 176vc, 211vc.<date>18th
                           century</date>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Name of St Mary; names of the donors and of the
                           scribe (not always); the word salām; other words: za-ʾaqǝräbku (fol. 78vb
                           l.38), nagaśt (fol. 140rc l.11), ba-sǝbḥata (fol. 157rb l.9), ba-qal
                           (fol. 194va l.2); incipits of the text and its sections (a few lines are
                           rubricated, alternating with black lines, at the beginning of each
                           monthly reading: fols. 3r, 40r, 70r, 103r, 142r, 184v); elements of the
                           punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h2" script="Ethiopic">- The marker of the 6th order of ጵ is
                        attached to the to the upper vertical stroke (e.g. ኢትዮጵያ, <locus target="#3rb">3rb</locus> l.5, ቆጵርያኖስ, <locus target="#31rb">31rb</locus>
                        l.3).</handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h3" script="Ethiopic"> - The number 9 (፱) is shaped as ፀ
                        (e.g. <locus target="#16rc">16rc</locus> l.15, 30ra
                        l.32).</handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h4" script="Ethiopic"> - The number 1 (፩) is particularly
                        rounded and upwards-oriented (e.g. <locus target="#3ra">3ra</locus> l.1,
                        11ra
                        l.10).</handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#1va">f. 1va-1</locus>
                           <desc>vb: Note, unclear.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus from="1va" to="1vb">1va-1vb</locus>: ወርኃ፡ ጥቅምት፡ ቡሩክ፡ መዓ፡ የሐፅጽ፡
